50|$|The Apple II {{video output}} {{is really a}} <b>monochrome</b> <b>display</b> based upon the bit {{patterns}} in the video memory (or pixels). These pixels are combined in quadrature with the colorburst signal to be interpreted as color by a composite video display.|$|R
